The Intimacy Project 
A Practical and Personalised Life Support System
1:1 Life Support and Guidance

David & Ana have been travelling, studying and practicing with different teachers across the world for the last 10 years, and specialise in supporting students to create and maintain a daily practice that brings harmony and balance to life.

Over the past few years they have been working with students 1:1 to help bring about positive change in their lives.

How do they do that?
By using various tools that help to balance the internal system to bring harmony, care and love into life.
They draw upon their own experience and trainings in yoga asana, pranayama, meditation, Qi-Gong, nutrition, compassion and by creating a space completely free of judgement. They believe each of us has a gift, and learning to express this in life is all part of the practice. From here, positive changes can begin....read more

Growing up, Thomas lived with a rare chronic, autoimmune disorder that resulted in seizures and other painful neurological symptoms. It shaped who he was and who he has become.
Unfortunately, like many people, Western Medicine did not provide any real healing. 
That’s when he decided to take his health into his own hands.
Thomas enrolled in acupuncture & Chinese Medicine school and spent countless hours training with high level masters in qigong, taijiquan and meditation. It was a long journey that taught him about true healing and wellness.
It was this path that helped me find my passion–ensuring others find their own path to healing. Now, Thomas is fulfilling that passion as a Holistic Coach and licensed practitioner of Chinese Medicine, acupuncture, and herbal and dietary therapy. He is also had the honor of becoming a certified qigong healer and teacher.
